                    The limit of zones delineated a jurisdictions of coastline encompassing the baseline, internal waters, territorial seas, economic exclusive zone, and continental shelf and overlapping zones between neighbors’ states.
                </p>
                <br>
                <p style="  font-size: 21px;">

                    <b> Maritime Zones </b>
                </p>

                <p>
                    Issued in 1982, the Law of the Sea regulates ocean and sea space into maritime zones, that a state may clAims rights. These zones are divided into six zones as follows:
                </p>



            </div>




            <div class="container mt-1">
                <div id="accordion">



                    <div class="card">
