                                <img src="~/Images/tick-m.PNG" width="20">
                            </a>
                        </div>
                        <div id="collapsefour" class="collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordion">
                            <div class="card-body">



                                The UNCLOS Articles from (55 to 75) defines legal regime of this regard. (?) . Whether costal or land locked, the end of EEZ is the median line.
                                <br /><br />
                                The sovereign in a state has special rights regarding the exploration and use of marine resources of the seabed as fishery and minerals and with
                                regard to other activities for the economic exploitation and managing the natural resources whether living or nonliving. Meanwhile, this law gives
                                other states access to the surplus of the allowable resources.
                                <br /><br />






                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>






                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-header backBlue d-flex justify-content-between hovertitle" data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#collapsefive">
