                                Which are comprised of all parts of the sea that are not under any state control, excluding the internal waters, the territorial seas, EEZ and archipelagic waters, as set in Article (86).
                                <br /><br />






                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>



                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>



